(121, '', '<div class=\"aboutus-banner banner-image\">\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Az egyes&uuml;let tev&eacute;kenys&eacute;ge:</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A Honv&eacute;d Ez&uuml;st Ny&iacute;l Sportegyes&uuml;let 1958-ban alakult azzal a c&eacute;llal, hogy stabil h&aacute;tteret biztos&iacute;tson a sportolni v&aacute;gy&oacute;, eg&eacute;szs&eacute;ges &eacute;letm&oacute;dot folytat&oacute; szem&eacute;lyek r&eacute;sz&eacute;re. Egyes&uuml;let&uuml;nk c&eacute;lcsoportja sz&eacute;les k&ouml;rű. Nemtől, kort&oacute;l, t&aacute;rsadalmi &eacute;s szoci&aacute;lis helyzettől f&uuml;ggetlen&uuml;l v&aacute;runk &eacute;s fogadunk mindenkit, aki az egyes&uuml;let alapszab&aacute;ly&aacute;t elfogadja. Minden tag r&eacute;sz&eacute;re egyenlően, lehetős&eacute;geinkhez m&eacute;rten biztos&iacute;tjuk a sportol&aacute;s felt&eacute;teleit.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Fő eredm&eacute;nyeink, legfontosabb projektjeink:</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Felsorolni neh&eacute;z a korl&aacute;tozott terjedelem mellett az elm&uacute;lt &eacute;vtizedek eredm&eacute;nyeinek bemutat&aacute;s&aacute;t. Dr. Simicsk&oacute; Istv&aacute;n Honv&eacute;delmi Miniszter, mint HM parlamenti &aacute;llamtitk&aacute;r, &Aacute;llamtitk&aacute;ri D&iacute;szoklevelet adom&aacute;nyozott az egyes&uuml;let r&eacute;sz&eacute;re az amatőr sportbajnoks&aacute;gok, versenyek szervez&eacute;se ter&uuml;let&eacute;n &eacute;s az ifj&uacute;s&aacute;g honv&eacute;delmi nevel&eacute;s&eacute;ben v&eacute;gzett kiv&aacute;l&oacute; sportegyes&uuml;leti munk&aacute;&eacute;rt.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Az egyes&uuml;let a bev&eacute;teleit rendezv&eacute;nyeinek szervez&eacute;s&eacute;re ford&iacute;tva. </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Főbb, (rendszeres) rendezv&eacute;nyeink az elm&uacute;lt &eacute;vben:</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">1. Military Survival Run &ndash; Akad&aacute;lyfut&oacute; Verseny szervez&eacute;se ( m&aacute;r 2010 &oacute;ta, t&ouml;bb mint 300 fő r&eacute;szv&eacute;tel&eacute;vel)</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">2.Gyermekt&aacute;bor (2007 &oacute;ta, &eacute;vente 30-35 gyermek r&eacute;szv&eacute;tel&eacute;vel)</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">3.Honv&eacute;delmi Ifj&uacute;s&aacute;gi Verseny (2010 &oacute;ta &aacute;tlagosan 15 k&ouml;z&eacute;p &eacute;s &aacute;ltal&aacute;nos iskola r&eacute;szv&eacute;tel&eacute;vel!)</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">4.Term&eacute;szetj&aacute;r&oacute; t&uacute;r&aacute;k. A term&eacute;szetj&aacute;r&oacute; szakoszt&aacute;ly rendszeresen j&aacute;rja haz&aacute;nk nevezetes &eacute;s sz&eacute;p helyeit. Egy &aacute;tlagos &eacute;vben t&ouml;bb mint 20 t&uacute;r&aacute;t teljes&iacute;tenek a Bakonyban, a Soproni &eacute;s a Kőszegi-hegys&eacute;gben.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">5. VulcanRun &ndash; akad&aacute;lyfut&aacute;s id&eacute;n elősz&ouml;r, t&ouml;bb mint 200 indul&oacute;val.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">6. VulcanRun- terepfut&oacute; verseny id&eacute;n novemberben!</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Mutat&oacute;sz&aacute;maink:</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Versenyeinkről besz&aacute;mol rendszeresen a Veszpr&eacute;m Megyei Napl&oacute;, a p&aacute;pai honlap (papa-ma), a hososz.hu, a honvedelem.hu honlapon is megjelen&uuml;nk. A napl&oacute; 35 000-es p&eacute;ld&aacute;nysz&aacute;mban jelenik meg, olvas&oacute;sz&aacute;ma 129 000 fő. Rendezv&eacute;nyeink megtekinthetők a P&aacute;pa V&aacute;rosi T&eacute;v&eacute;ben, Veszpr&eacute;m TV-ben (t&ouml;bb mint 2000-en tekintett&eacute;k meg a legutols&oacute; vide&oacute;t a t&eacute;v&eacute; youtube csatorn&aacute;j&aacute;n).</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Egy kis visszaigazol&oacute;: http://ocrmagazin.blog.hu/2017/12/31/sebok_szabolcs_top5_o</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Azt hiszem ez is igen j&oacute;l mutatja a rendezv&eacute;ny&uuml;nk siker&eacute;t, beletett rengetett munk&aacute;t.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A Hungarian Military Survival Run Facebook oldalunknak 2018. okt&oacute;ber&eacute;ben 2147 k&ouml;vetője van, bejegyz&eacute;seinkkel t&ouml;bb, mint 19000 el&eacute;r&eacute;st dokument&aacute;lhatunk.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Versenyeink nagyfok&uacute; felk&eacute;sz&uuml;lts&eacute;get k&iacute;v&aacute;nnak a jelentkezőktől, de a term&eacute;szetj&aacute;r&oacute; t&uacute;r&aacute;ink k&ouml;nnyed kikapcsol&oacute;d&aacute;sra is lehetős&eacute;get ad.</span></span></span></span></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"sub-content\">\n<p><strong>Ez&uuml;st Ny&iacute;l Sportegyes&uuml;let</strong></p>\n\n<div class=\"align-center bg-gray container\">\n<p>C&iacute;m: 8500 P&aacute;pa, Vaszari &uacute;t 101.<br />\nE-mail:&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:survivalrun.hu@gmail.com\">survivalrun.hu@gmail.com</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n', 'hu', '2018-10-05 09:22:46', 0),
