(166, 'vulcanrun', '<div class=\"sub-content\">\n<h1>Inform&aacute;ci&oacute;k</h1>\n\n<p><strong>C&eacute;lja</strong>: Az eg&eacute;szs&eacute;ges &eacute;letm&oacute;d megszerettet&eacute;se, a k&ouml;z&ouml;s sportol&aacute;s, a fut&aacute;s n&eacute;pszerűs&iacute;t&eacute;se, versenyz&eacute;si lehetős&eacute;g biztos&iacute;t&aacute;sa amatőr&ouml;knek &eacute;s profiknak egyar&aacute;nt. Szeretn&eacute;l felk&eacute;sz&uuml;lni a k&ouml;vetkező VulcanRun terep-akad&aacute;lyfut&oacute; versenyre, vagy csak szeretn&eacute;l egy kicsit sportolni a term&eacute;szetben? Akkor itt indulnod kell! :-D&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><strong>D&aacute;tum:</strong> 2018.11.24.<br />\n<strong>Helysz&iacute;n: </strong>Celld&ouml;m&ouml;lk, S&aacute;ghegyalja k&ouml;r&uacute;t 1.</p>\n\n<p><strong>T&aacute;vok:&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>5 km 115m emelked&eacute;s</li>\n	<li>10 km 230m emelked&eacute;s</li>\n	<li>15 km 345m emelked&eacute;s</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Kateg&oacute;ri&aacute;k:</strong></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">Egy&eacute;ni:&nbsp;</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>Női: -18, 19-34, 35-49, 50+</li>\n	<li>F&eacute;rfi: -18, 19-34, 35-49, 50+</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:40px\">V&aacute;lt&oacute;:</p>\n\n<ul style=\"margin-left:40px\">\n	<li>3x5 km-es v&aacute;lt&oacute;: 3 versenyző 1-1 k&ouml;r ideje alapj&aacute;n az &ouml;sszes&iacute;tett idő sz&aacute;m&iacute;t</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Korhat&aacute;r:</strong><strong> </strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Csak a 12 &eacute;vet bet&ouml;lt&ouml;tt szem&eacute;lyek indulhatnak a versenyen. 12 &eacute;v alatt csak sz&uuml;lői fel&uuml;gyelettel.</span></span></p>\n\n<p><strong>D&iacute;jaz&aacute;s:</strong><br />\nMinden kateg&oacute;ria 1-3 helyezettje d&iacute;jaz&aacute;sban r&eacute;szes&uuml;l.</p>\n\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Időrend:</span></span></strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">09.00: Regisztr&aacute;ci&oacute; megnyit&aacute;sa</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Rajt időpontok</span></span></span></span>\n	<ul>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">10.00: 15 km</span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">10.15: 10 km</span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ul>\n	</li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A 10 &eacute;s 15 km-es t&aacute;v indul&aacute;sa &ouml;sszevonhat&oacute; egy időpontba, amennyiben kevesebb nevező van</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">10.30: 5 km</span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">A 3x5 kil&oacute;m&eacute;teres v&aacute;lt&oacute; első tagjai is 10.00-kor indul. A v&aacute;lt&oacute; k&ouml;vetkező tagja a c&eacute;l előtt kijel&ouml;lt v&aacute;lt&oacute; z&oacute;n&aacute;ban kell, hogy bev&aacute;rja &eacute;s v&aacute;ltsa az előtte fut&oacute;t. Eredm&eacute;ny&uuml;ket az &ouml;sszes&iacute;tett idej&uuml;k adja.</span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br />\n<strong>Nevez&eacute;si d&iacute;j:</strong></p>\n\n<table>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.25pt\">&nbsp;</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.25pt\"><strong>5 km</strong></td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.3pt\"><strong>10 km</strong></td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.3pt\"><strong>15 km</strong></td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.25pt\">Előnevez&eacute;s</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.25pt\">3500 Ft</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.3pt\">4000 Ft</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.3pt\">4500 Ft</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.25pt\">Helysz&iacute;ni</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.25pt\">4500 Ft</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.3pt\">5000 Ft</td>\n			<td style=\"text-align:center; vertical-align:top; width:113.3pt\">5500 Ft</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p><strong>Nevez&eacute;s okt&oacute;ber 5-től:</strong>&nbsp;<a data-lynx-mode=\"hover\" href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.survivalrun.hu%2F&amp;h=AT2JSRPnA_Kr4JKmmwbl2_8QQKX5-qdBDHAyrCr35a19QStMIaIiVVs192I7fMCrC_NoFpP2caddJNFQzRpL_4zqK3bnNJ8uF3rsNsfWDxgM6P2QBFozTEmFshT23mpXpg\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">www.survivalrun.hu</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Ha v&aacute;lt&oacute;ban szeretn&eacute;l indulni, azt csak az oldalra reg