e:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica\\,Arial\\,sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">&eacute;gig a mez</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">őny előtt</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica\\,Arial\\,sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">- Zuhanyz&aacute;si, &ouml;lt&ouml;z&eacute;si lehet</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">ős</span></span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica\\,Arial\\,sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">&eacute;g<br />\n- Orvosi fel&uuml;gyelet a versenyen&nbsp;<br />\n- Kateg&oacute;ri&aacute;nk&eacute;nti d&iacute;jaz&aacute;st minden t&aacute;von</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica\\,Arial\\,sans-serif&quot;\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">- Abszol&uacute;t 1-3. helyezettek k&uuml;l&ouml;n d&iacute;jaz&aacute;sa minden t&aacute;von.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"><span style=\"color:#0d0d0d\">Az &uacute;tvonal v&eacute;gig biztos&iacute;tva, a fordul&oacute;pontok t&aacute;bl&aacute;val jelezve lesznek.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt\"