ont-size:12.0pt\">14+: Minimum 14 kil&oacute;m&eacute;teres t&aacute;v, 400-500 m szintk&uuml;l&ouml;nbs&eacute;g, min. 22 akad&aacute;ly</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><strong><u><span style=\"font-size:14.0pt\">A verseny időrendje:</span></u></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">08.30-10.30: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Regisztr&aacute;ci&oacute;</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">09.30-t&oacute;l: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Futamok rajtjai, csoportokban </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">A l&eacute;tsz&aacute;m f&uuml;ggv&eacute;ny&eacute;ben ker&uuml;l meghat&aacute;roz&aacute;sra, futamonk&eacute;nt 30-50 fő.</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">Első hull&aacute;mban a 14+, majd a 7+ rajtjai k&ouml;vetkeznek </span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\">14.00-15.00:&nbsp